~FT+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+
~FT   Command~RS  : muzzle                                    ~FTRNUTS Version 3.0.2
~FT+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+

~FT   Usage~RS    : muzzle <username>

   Muzzles a user which prevents them speaking, shouting, emoting and 
   mailing other people. The muzzle levels are based upon the user 
   level of whoever muzzled the user. If a user is muzzled by a wizard 
   for instance he can be unmuzzled by and archwiz or a god, if however 
   he is muzzled by a god only another god can unmuzzle him.

~FT+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+
~FT   See also~RS : unmuzzle, arrest, release
~FT+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+
